1. blend 1/2 cup granulated sugar with 2 cups flour
2. knead in 1.5 cubes of Land-O-Lakes butter. It is important to use the best butter (salted).
3. Press into cookie sheet.
4. Bake at 350F until some sign of browning appears around the edges. 
5. Cut into cookies while still hot.
6. Let cool at room temp.
7. Separate the cookies and enjoy!
